<!--
  Phase 7.46: canonical sitemap.
  - Domain is virtualfit.app, NOT the anonymous Azure SWA preview hostname
    (wonderful-sky-...azurestaticapps.net) the file used to ship. Crawlers
    indexing the Azure URL split SEO equity from the real domain and
    broadcast a throwaway hostname as canonical.
  - Every directory under app/ with a routable page.tsx is listed.
    /checkout/success/ is intentionally omitted (post-purchase thank-you,
    not for indexing — Phase 7.75 also gave it a robots: noindex,nofollow
    meta tag for defense in depth).
  - Phase 7.76: dropped /retailer/ from the sitemap entirely. Phase 7.61
    permanently redirects it to /retailer/signup; listing the redirect
    source AND the redirect target wasted crawl budget and confused
    canonical signal. Only /retailer/signup/ remains. Also bumped
    lastmod to 2026-04-25 across the board.
-->
